01

Description

The Backpack is made of polyester fabric with a water-repellent matt coating. With a capacity of 25 litres, it can support a weight of up to 10 kg. The shoulder straps and backs are padded but perforated to increase breathability, which is always critical in the back area where the backpack rests. Complete with three compartments, one of which is padded and dedicated to the PC. Two side pockets in mesh and stretch fabric. The zips opening the sectors are concealed for greater protection. The dimensions are 51x31x20 cm.

02

Product details

  • Backpack with 25 litre capacity made of polyester fabric with water-repellent matt coating
  • Three compartments with a padded PC pocket
  • Side pockets with elastic insert
  • Front elastic drawcord system
  • Padded back and shoulder straps in contrasting colour, perforated for greater breathability
  • Reflective logo prints
  • Dimensions: 51x31x20 cm, 25 litres, maximum load 10 Kg
